|3 |    └─WINDOW FUNCTION                |        |
|4 |      └─PARTITION SORT               |        |
|5 |        └─EXCHANGE IN DISTR          |        |
|6 |          └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (HASH)|:EX10000|
|7 |            └─PX BLOCK ITERATOR      |        |
|8 |              └─TABLE FULL SCAN      |TEST1   |
===================================================
